group settings 
so that messages from new members will be moderated.  If this doesn't
fix the 
problem, I'll make all messages moderated. My apologies for the
inconvenience.

supporting flame 
simulations in Matlab have been delayed a bit, due to the demands of
various other 
projects. Hopefully it will happen in a week or two.
